<ul>
<li><b>Agnus Dei</b>, text as the <i><a href="/wiki/Agnus_Dei" title="Agnus Dei">Agnus Dei</a></i> in the Ordinary of the <a href="/wiki/Mass_(music)" title="Mass (music)">Mass</a>, but with the petitions <i>miserere nobis</i> changed to <i>dona eis requiem</i>, and <i>dona nobis pacem</i> to <i>dona eis requiem sempiternam</i>:</li>
